                                                                                        <TextBlock>
                                                                                            When a script is loaded for this axis<LineBreak/>
                                                                                            and motion provider is running<LineBreak/>
                                                                                            the output value will be a blend of those two<LineBreak/>
                                                                                            based on the slider below
                                                                                        </TextBlock>
